How to Choose:
Start with Simpler Projects: Choose projects that focus on basic concepts like DOM manipulation and event handling (e.g., To-Do List, Tip Calculator).
Move to Intermediate Projects: Once comfortable, try projects involving APIs or more complex logic (e.g., Weather App, Quiz App).
Work on Your Game Idea: With some practice, you'll be ready to tackle your game project, combining what you've learned.
Choose one from the list, and I can guide you through the process!